<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>What this does:</strong> This is the Factory. ShoppingCart will call this instead of doing if-else itself. Notice ShoppingCart no longer needs to know about any discount class — it just asks the factory and gets back a <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">DiscountStrategy</code> object.</p>
