</span></span><span>Factory Method
</span><span>
</span><span>## Why This Pattern
</span><span>ShoppingCart was handling discount logic internally with if-else blocks,
</span><span>violating OCP and SRP. 
</span><span>
</span><span>## What Changed
</span><span>- Extracted DiscountStrategy interface
</span><span>- Created separate class for each discount type
</span><span>- Created DiscountFactory to centralize object creation
</span><span>- ShoppingCart now only calls the factory
</span><span>
</span><span>## Closes
</span><span>Closes #1</span></code></pre></div></div>
