<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Good news — your <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">DiscountStrategy</code> interface from Phase 1 is the perfect base for Decorator. We just need a few new classes.</p>
