<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>What this does:</strong> A concrete observer that prints cart events to the console. In a real app you could have other observers like <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">EmailObserver</code> or <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">LogObserver</code> — they'd all implement the same interface but do different things.</p>
