span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> AI Log — Phase 3: Behavioral Patterns</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Prompt I Asked</span><span>
</span></span><span>"Strategy ve Observer pattern'leri bu projede nerede kullanılabilir? 
</span><span>Hangisi daha önce uygulanmalı?"
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> AI's Answer (Summary)</span><span>
</span></span><span>AI recommended implementing Observer first to add event notifications 
</span><span>to the cart, then Strategy to formalize discount selection. Observer 
</span><span>was suggested to notify on item additions and discount applications. 
</span><span>Strategy was already partially applied in Phase 1 via Factory Method — 
</span><span>Phase 3 completes it by using strategy objects directly instead of 
</span><span>string-based selection.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> What I Implemented and Why</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Pattern 1: Observer</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Where:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`CartObserver.java`</span><span>, </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`ConsoleObserver.java`</span><span>, updated </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`ShoppingCart.java`</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Why:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> To notify listeners when cart events happen (item added, 
</span></span><span>discount applied) without ShoppingCart needing to know who is listening.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">###</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Pattern 2: Strategy (completed)</span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Where:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`DiscountStrategy.java`</span><span> and all discount classes
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Why:</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> Strategy was introduced in Phase 1 but completed here — 
</span></span><span>discount objects are now passed directly instead of using string keys.
</span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Where AI Was Wrong or Incomplete</span><span>
</span></span><span>[write 2 honest lines here — did anything not work as expected? 
</span><span>Did you have to adjust anything?]</span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Fill in the last section, save, then tell me when ready to commit!</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
