</span></span><span><span class="token token table table-data-rows"></span><span>
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Mimari Diyagram</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(234, 236, 240);">!</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">[</span><span class="token token content" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">UML Diyagramı</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">](</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">docs/diagrams/architecture.png</span><span class="token token" style="color: rgb(94, 237, 237);">)</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Nasıl Çalıştırılır</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">1.</span><span> Eclipse'de projeyi açın
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">2.</span><span> </span><span class="token token code-snippet code" style="color: rgb(204, 123, 244);">`src/main.java`</span><span> dosyasına sağ tıklayın
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">3.</span><span> </span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span class="token token bold content">Run As → Java Application</span><span class="token token bold" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">**</span><span> seçin
</span></span><span><span></span><span class="token token list" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">4.</span><span> Konsol çıktısını inceleyin
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token hr" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">---</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222); font-weight: bold;">##</span><span class="token token title" style="color: rgb(244, 123, 133); font-weight: bold;"> Proje Yapısı</span><span>
</span></span><span>
</span><span><span></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code code-block">eticaret-sepeti/
</span></span><span>├── README.md
</span><span>├── PATTERNS.md
</span><span>├── PROBLEMS.md
</span><span>├── src/
</span><span>│   ├── main.java
</span><span>│   ├── Item.java
</span><span>│   ├── ShoppingCart.java
</span><span>│   ├── DiscountStrategy.java
</span><span>│   ├── DiscountFactory.java
</span><span>│   ├── WelcomeDiscount.java
</span><span>│   ├── BlackFridayDiscount.java
</span><span>│   ├── Over100Discount.java
</span><span>│   ├── Buy2Get1Discount.java
</span><span>│   ├── DiscountDecorator.java
</span><span>│   ├── WelcomeDecorator.java
</span><span>│   ├── BlackFridayDecorator.java
</span><span>│   ├── CheckoutFacade.java
</span><span>│   ├── CartObserver.java
</span><span>│   └── ConsoleObserver.java
</span><span>└── docs/
</span><span>    ├── diagrams/
</span><span><span class="token token code code-block">    └── ai-log/</span><span class="token token code">
</span></span><span><span class="token token code"></span><span class="token token code" style="color: rgb(211, 215, 222);">```</span></span></code></pre></div></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Save it. Done?</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><div class="w-fit" data-state="closed"><button class="inline-flex
